{"tid":2079125,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得立場新出篇報道係想造龍門？","createTime":"2020-06-25T14:37:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T07:35:31.000Z","uid":97941,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4d349ad8f669415db1ac0a8b90653834241c43cb","tid":2079125,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:37:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3204052526347012/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3204052526347012%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SqkErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=bbb7b901\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3204052526347012/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n我本身睇標題同頭幾段都正路<br />\n但後面內文鬼鬼地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//張回應說，由於他未能以中心名義成功申請到任何銀行戶口，所以盆菜及糕餅的收入，都是以龍門餐飲有限公司兩個戶口代收，稱該兩個戶口只會獨立處理中心的收入及支出，與龍門冰室的支出及收入沒有抵觸。不過，他後來說中心的資金不足，有不少項目都是由龍門先墊支推動，事後再從該兩個「獨立戶口」取回成本，換言之龍門帳戶及「獨立帳戶」有資金往來。//<br />\n<br />\n明明張老板已經講明龍門同資源中心盤數唔關事<br />\n篇文仲要夾硬講兜到有關係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//張亦指，因為未收齊年糕、盆菜等款項而要為防疫物品墊支。防疫項目於 1 月 20 開始，由龍門墊支購入 1000 盒台灣口罩，而其提供的報表顯示，他於 12 月有1,400多萬收益，在扣除 12 月及 1 月的所有開支，仍有300多萬盈餘。《立場新聞》曾向張俊傑查詢為何中心在一月有盈餘的情況下，還要龍門向中心墊支，惟張俊傑指已十數次回覆報道，而且公事繁忙，未有再作任何回應。//<br />\n<br />\n仲有呢個位都好似特登針對張老板<br />\n又係challenge佢講法⋯⋯<br />\n仲要查詢十幾次煩到老板唔再回應<br />\n究竟立場係發生乜事<br />\n咁多嘢唔報反而好似一齊鬥黃咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3411f20068b8610988ae3bb6efebf0a90befd12d","tid":2079125,"uid":195998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:38:46.000Z","msg":"300多萬盈餘"},{"pid":"3dbde729afd363dd98ca24065f587209a0422a62","tid":2079125,"uid":97941,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:40:06.000Z","msg":"以後係咪淨係可以睇蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54c00769462236387fd0a55345b6e7a29ae072c","tid":2079125,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6083469baaa27fcaaa39a2695bf1e06a19d1f7","tid":2079125,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69fda8c83e73e17bce8220376c5f01d56b9e713","tid":2079125,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:42:36.000Z","msg":"時事台冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668e68bbbbad113ddf943752f48cfd2432da0e83","tid":2079125,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670201b9d8b1da99728e66dc8d1f5a04eac7143a","tid":2079125,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc35896a151dc1c65710547e468dba7ba8f00570","tid":2079125,"uid":115579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3411f20068b8610988ae3bb6efebf0a90befd12d","tid":2079125,"uid":195998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:38:46.000Z","msg":"300多萬盈餘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:45:47.000Z","msg":"黄色慈善圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e51d2ad8b005462e2a75c3c8186146f6578b11","tid":2079125,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29acf6466b768af03d2707d6670491f1d5729df","tid":2079125,"uid":51583,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:46:19.000Z","msg":"我覺得龍門乜都解釋晒<br />\n攤晒出黎比大家睇<br />\n好多都係對家想借龍門賺大錢<br />\n宜家都仲有唔少人同佢合作緊但都係真係為手足的"},{"pid":"ed9276494aeda162d7f75f21692aab7fa27ab490","tid":2079125,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dc35896a151dc1c65710547e468dba7ba8f00570","tid":2079125,"uid":115579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3411f20068b8610988ae3bb6efebf0a90befd12d","tid":2079125,"uid":195998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:38:46.000Z","msg":"300多萬盈餘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:45:47.000Z","msg":"黄色慈善圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:46:25.000Z","msg":"張老板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eacab72b18085e0935a7f4c75c8619bdde5b566","tid":2079125,"uid":113074,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:47:15.000Z","msg":"黎智英插黃之鋒<br />\n立場咪插龍門囉<br />\n<br />\n你一拳我一腳嘅嘢  大家扮唔明咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9a8af20d753c8f8c33480a3ac5551153e53438","tid":2079125,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0eacab72b18085e0935a7f4c75c8619bdde5b566","tid":2079125,"uid":113074,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:47:15.000Z","msg":"黎智英插黃之鋒<br />\n立場咪插龍門囉<br />\n<br />\n你一拳我一腳嘅嘢  大家扮唔明咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"唔通立場同龍門有仇口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1515a80ca42d76450211b3de20de80258cf1585c","tid":2079125,"uid":114891,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T14:52:28.000Z","msg":"篇文個格式係<br />\nB指控A論點1<br />\nA受訪澄清<br />\nB指控A論點2<br />\nA受訪澄清<br />\n唔好亂鳩講比人以為分化啦"},{"pid":"1fea7f6b9f0d78517d18000845bf05a239d31490","tid":2079125,"uid":208227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T17:30:17.000Z","msg":"報導其中一個重點係龍門先斬後奏用咗本來預備幫手足嘅錢去做「抗疫 」，仲要「抗疫」物資來源有問題喎。"},{"pid":"ec68a510304fd93cc1e416d42530259d24017a8b","tid":2079125,"uid":318505,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T18:41:02.000Z","msg":"立場都係如實講姐<br />\n畢竟件事都糾纏咁耐，早啲有個了結都好<br />\n其實張生暫時第一篇大部分我覺得都解釋到<br />\n係第二篇最大質疑係搞中心嘅錢去左填防疫數，<br />\n籌幾多唔洗逐項交代我接受，<br />\n但冇即刻交代籌嘅用途改左就難免有爭議<br />\n雖然比我蝕咁多都想拎去填數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a735de89c5e6e1a46ddf4bff4a9d3890ebddbe2","tid":2079125,"uid":167992,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T19:50:01.000Z","msg":"比我都嬲嘅，啲家長義務幫手，本黎諗住幫手足比律師費，變成變龍門填防疫氹。"},{"pid":"71daa5f72e8cba4d76c433e7bbdf7fe44a0dd31d","tid":2079125,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T19:51:01.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"be69f9f2a6594a3bbea36f7e03fea76901b0205e","tid":2079125,"uid":236414,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1fea7f6b9f0d78517d18000845bf05a239d31490","tid":2079125,"uid":208227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T17:30:17.000Z","msg":"報導其中一個重點係龍門先斬後奏用咗本來預備幫手足嘅錢去做「抗疫 」，仲要「抗疫」物資來源有問題喎。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T20:23:27.000Z","msg":"睇咗成篇文，立場都算報導得公正。<br />\n<br />\n其實唔好話立場造唔造龍門，見到成篇內文有好多位都係張俊傑不願透露，<br />\n口罩、韓國洗手液、越南皮下注射器呢幾part更加不知所謂。<br />\nPress要求證，查詢多幾次攞多啲資訊個問題又係邊？<br />\n<br />\n另外如果樓主覺得淨係可以睇蘋果嘅話，<br />\n我可以講蘋果嘅FC能力、記者文筆比起立場仲差，<br />\n有心求證一件事唔應該淨係睇一個傳媒。"},{"pid":"1683b5f26485ae855d9d19136304486c8d08a231","tid":2079125,"uid":210006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T20:33:57.000Z","msg":"份報道咪陳述緊事實 有咩問題？ <br />\n全部字都好中性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48311cfa64cfaf85ed8890454de268c85f935772","tid":2079125,"uid":14941,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T03:08:42.000Z","msg":"龍門老闆真係有啲野....."},{"pid":"233716a73c5921ca321ea7e546db1c47693825a7","tid":2079125,"uid":141033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:43:52.000Z","msg":"做龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登仔好趣緻"},{"pid":"ae8166bca1fbf0466d07dbab4e0b717f0a769af0","tid":2079125,"uid":34811,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:05:35.000Z","msg":"你死la<br />\n連登唔可以對龍門有任何質疑"},{"pid":"433daab06b5fe0b792200127f434097f3a58f1c9","tid":2079125,"uid":110641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"233716a73c5921ca321ea7e546db1c47693825a7","tid":2079125,"uid":141033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T07:43:52.000Z","msg":"做龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登仔好趣緻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T21:12:05.000Z","msg":"成班極反智盲撐人血張。"}]}